# Application functionality

## Repeat
When the user has reached the completion page and has NOT completed with 100% score, then the user need to go through all steps again, in sequence.

Those of the steps which the user failed have to be answered again.

Those that was completed there will just be a (blue) next button, and the correct answer highlighted.

After all failed has been answered again, the score must be calculated again on the completion page.

The engine must do the calculation of the score and which step to do next.


